# {{cx|Beginning Mandarin|lang=zh|sort=ma5}} final interrogative particle on a yes/no question
#: {{zh-usex|你 喜歡 嗎？|Do you like it?|link=y}}

====Usage notes====
The particule 嗎 allow to turn an affirmative sentence into a interrogative sentence without modifying the sentence order.
:: 他喜歡。 He likes it.
:: 他喜歡'''嗎'''? '''Does''' he like it?

